# Gapminder example 2

```{r, fig=TRUE, fig.height=3, fig.width=9, out.width="100%", fig.align="center", dev="svg"}
g2 <- ggplot(gm4, aes(x=year, y=gdpPercap)) + 
  geom_line() +
  facet_wrap(~country, nrow=1) + 
  theme_bw() + 
  labs(x="Year", y="GDP/capita", colour="Country")
g2
```

